hopobject.body: I've been cut off medicalbillingandcoding.org Ambitious targets for sure. However, there is nothing in the update that blows Whitbread’s strategy off course. For investors that means double-digit earnings and dividend growth for five years if those targets are met. That is because Mr Harrison said capital expenditure plans at Premier Inn are set to stay in line with new rooms growth, and he also expects to hold dividend cover at 2.5 times earnings.
